          My work blends CAD, simulation, testing, and iteration to move concepts from sketch to validated hardware.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button primary" href="#projects">View Projects</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="#">Download Resume</a>
