              <button class="icon-btn" id="prev" aria-label="Previous slide">←</button>
              <button class="icon-btn" id="next" aria-label="Next slide">→</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Compact fixture redesign</h3>
            <p>
              Redesigned a benchtop fixture to improve stiffness, reduce mass, and simplify assembly.
              The project combined CAD iteration, tolerance review, prototype validation, and design-for-manufacturing decisions.
            </p>
            <div class="details">
              <div class="detail">
                <strong>Problem</strong>
                Reduce weight and improve repeatability without increasing part count.
              </div>
              <div class="detail">
                <strong>Role</strong>
                Led concept generation, CAD modeling, prototype fabrication, and test planning.
              </div>
              <div class="detail">
                <strong>Tools</strong>
                SolidWorks, caliper-based inspection, 3D printing, Excel test logging.
              </div>
              <div class="detail">
                <strong>Outcome</strong>
                18% lighter assembly and faster alignment during bench setup.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
